@SeoAudit.Api_HostAddress = http://localhost:5113
@FirebaseIdToken = paste-firebase-id-token-here

GET {{SeoAudit.Api_HostAddress}}/health
Accept: application/json

###

POST {{SeoAudit.Api_HostAddress}}/api/auth/session
Authorization: Bearer {{FirebaseIdToken}}
Accept: application/json

###

GET {{SeoAudit.Api_HostAddress}}/api/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{FirebaseIdToken}}
Accept: application/json

###
